summary:
Specialties: Mapping processes to the best support by systems or applications, to achieve business goals.
Process areas are Supply chain, Logistics, production, QM and Maintenance. Integration to costing and financial areas.
Introduction new, web based ruled processes, with effective problem solving.
Since 1985 I worked on SAP related projects in:
Australia, Belgium, Brazil, Canada, China (PRC), Cura√ßao, Finland, Germany, Greece, India, Italy, Japan, New Zealand, Poland, Qatar, Saudi Arabia, Spain, Sweden, Turkey, UK, USA, The Netherlands.

KLM Royal Dutch Airlines. Inflight catering & entertainment Logistics & service delivery.
On request of KLM I continued to work on this project, after my retirement on May 31, 2017 until Jan 31, 2018.
Dutch Ministery IenM transformation to Risk based EAM
ArcelorMittal Mining. Strategic Proposal for Reliabillity based EAM.
Alliander, Quality control for Smart meters. SAP QM, MM, ISU Solution.
JCI, Process Template Build.
ArcelorMittal Tubular Products Saudia Arabia, Integration Roll.
AkzoNobel A&AC process interfaces for Logistic Service Providers.
Intertaste: Adapting SAP, Bespoke work for new LSP.
AkzoNobel Decorative paints Global roll out. PP-PI, PM, QM
Arizona Chemical Full Cycle. Europe and USA roll Out. PP-PI QM,PM, LE-WM
ChemChina, Building BBP process templates for future Roll out. PP-PI, PM, MM QM
SAP AG, Checking and Testing BBP for the Chemical, for Customer release 2008.
Training new Atos employees in PP, PP-PI, PM. For SAP certification. 95% Succes rate.
BAT, Template Based Full Cycle, PP-PI MM and LE-WM
Orica, Full Upgrade, Blue print, Australia, Germany. PP-PI, PM
Air services Australia, full cycle. PM PS.
Basell, Full implentation Cycle, Asia Pacific roll out. PP-PI, PM, LE
Vantico  Asia pacific rollout. PM, PP-PI, LE
Philips Medical, Customer Services
Andrew Corporation, Full Cycle. USA, Brazil and China (PRC) roll out. PP, PM
Occidental Chemical, Full Cycle. PM PP
and Much more!
